# ── Default-deny whitelist — hanya artefak publik yang ter-track ──
# Filosofi: tolak SEMUA dulu, izinkan eksplisit. File instruktur/rahasia
# (soal, rubrik, demo-script, runbook, rehearsal) tak pernah masuk git.
# GitHub Pages meng-serve repo ini di <user>.github.io/<repo>/

# sampah — selalu tolak
**/.DS_Store

# tolak semua di root repo
/*

# izinkan tooling + landing
!.gitignore
!.nojekyll
!index.html

# ── deck slide per minggu: izinkan folder, tolak isinya, izinkan slides/ ──
# (w04 sengaja TIDAK di-whitelist → deck battle w04 tetap LOCAL, soal aman)
!w01/
!w02/
!w03/
!w05/
w0*/*
!w01/slides/
!w02/slides/
!w03/slides/
!w05/slides/

# ── _shared: hanya dokumen peserta (bukan doc build-internal) ──
!_shared/
_shared/*
!_shared/silabus-vibe-coding.md
!_shared/versions.md
!_shared/seed/
!_shared/templates/
# build-week-handson.md · deck-engine.md · demo-script-pattern.md → LOCAL (tak di-whitelist)
